      "title": "Ruling party MPs to meet today (30)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A meeting of the members of the ruling party will be held today (30) at the Parliament.",
        "The meeting will be held under the leadership of President Ranil Wickramasinghe.",
        "Chief Government Whip and Minister Prasanna Ranatunga told News 1st that the discussions will focus on the current political situation and the Appropriation (Amendment) Bill."
      ],
